		    <td valign="top">
		    <p><font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    Brad posted the following update on the <a href="http://boards.station.sony.com/ubb/everquest/Forum1/HTML/000321.html"  >official boards</a>:
<blockquote>
<p>
Just an update on this, since it's been a while:
We'll be launching it in 'open beta' mode very soon, similar to how S. Zek initially was launched.</p>
<p>
As we get closer, we'll post the ruleset as it will be at beta launch.</p>
<p>
-Brad</p>
</blockquote>
