				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				For a true RPG server to work you will need the following in place:<BR>
1 - no /ooc, or /shout  when was the last time you shouted accross 2 miles to see what your friends were doing? THis will greatly enhance the rpg aspect of finding grups as well, taverns bars and Inns will become regular meeting areas, just like in a true RPG setting. <BR>
<BR>
2 - extend the /say radius to accomodate the loss of /ooc /shout.<BR>
<BR>
3 - set up customer service ppl to actually approve each name that goes through. That way you wont get stupid names like &quot;Ikickbutt Salot&quot; or &quot;Icangive Usow&quot;<BR>
