				I concur that the current /shout command should be scrapped; however I don't think it should be entirely removed.  It should be sort of an extended /say (which would negate any sort of need for an extension of /say range).  A better form of name-filtering is necessary, as those before me have already said.  I wonder if they will only allow one character on the server like on Sullon Zek to combat twinking? I am REALLY looking forward to this.  The concept of taverns having PEOPLE in them is really exciting for me, especially since I prefer to play bards.  
